===============================================================================
Release Status
===============================================================================
    - test on python 2.7            - done
    - run pylint                    - done
    - test on python 2.6
    - test automatically installing:
        - sqlalchemy
        - etc

===============================================================================
Primary Changes To Do:
===============================================================================
    - pypi
	- add appropriate precision to means, etc
	- setup testing?


===============================================================================
Primary Changes:
===============================================================================
    - general:
		- Changed division to future 
		- Added quite a bit of tests to test harnesses
    - gristle/metadata.py
        - initial appearance
        - added metadata library for the rest of the modules & scripts to store 
          results within
        - not yet integrated in a way that's useful however
    - gristle/simplesql.py
        - initial appearance
        - added library to minimize SQL necessary for testing & simple queries
    - gristle/preferences.py
        - initial appearance
        - added library to manage user configuration compliant with xdg spec
    - scripts/gristle_metadata.py
        - initial appearance
        - add api layer to manually CRUD metadata
    - scripts/gristle_validator.py
        - initial appearance
        - only provides ability to find records with invalid field number in 
          this release
	- gristle/field_misc.py 
		- ignores some garbage data, returns counts of bad rows found
 		- .strip() values put into frequency distributions
        - field_determinator.py 
		- handles bad data counts from field_misc.py
        - gristle_determinator.py
 		- added bad field count
		- widened field value width
	- scripts/gristle_file_converter.py
		- cleaned up the code
		- many misc improvements
        - gristle_freaker.py
                - completely rewritten - added ability to handle multiple
                  columns & sampling, also added test harness.
	- scripts/gristle_graphviz_generator.py
		- pulled out - it's just too immature

